stimulus:
Welcome! This experiment will last ~1 hour. In this experiment, you are the head captain of a pirate ship traveling around the world to different places. You will complete several different tasks during this experiment. Here is an overview of these tasks:


1. Tutorial and quiz

2. Pick a pirate game in 6 different places

3. Pick a pirate game and memory game

4. Final questions and payment


If you complete the entire experiment, you will receive $15 and you can earn up to $3 in bonus payments.

[Press the space bar to begin the tutorial]

You are the head captain of a pirate ship. Pirates rob other ships like the one below as they leave they leave the marketplace port. Ships leaving have just sold all their goods at the marketplace, so they have lots of gold on them.

[Press the space bar to continue]
